        "subject": "LU-15234 lnet: ref leak in lnet_ping_router_locked",
        "message": "LU-15234 lnet: ref leak in lnet_ping_router_locked\n\nIf lnet_update_rc_data_locked() returns NULL then there's a peer_ni\nreference leak in lnet_ping_router_locked(). Ensure the ref taken at\nbeginning of lnet_ping_router_locked() is dropped before the function\nreturns.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Chris Horn <chris.horn@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: I0364a9441c453c1ef53fed1103871581c64c6aeb\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_12"
    }
